## ▶ How It Works

The user is presented with a menu containing multiple options:

```text
1. Add Expenses
2. View all Expenses
3. Search Expense
4. Calculate Total Expense
5. Reset
6. Exit
```

The program stores expense data inside a Python dictionary and saves it to a local text file after updates so that previous expense history is not lost.

